tomkat center was created by stanford alumni tomkatcenter for sustainable energy stanford university pie precourt institute of energy stanford university search home about people connections research activities strategic interdisciplinary history goals of the tomkat center the tomkat center for sustainable energy works to transform the world's energy systems by identifying key challenges and defining research agendas carrying out evaluation and analysis challenging our faculty to form interdisciplinary groups to provide new approaches to problem solving developing methods for analysis that will be adopted by other practitioners performing systems level and cross disciplinary research facilitating translation to actual applied technology proposing innovative solutions the tomkat center was created in 2009 with a gift made by stanford alumni and husband and wife team tom steyer and kat taylor tomkat 2012 all rights reserved contact us terms of use facebook twitter
